<strong>Who=E2=80=99s included?</strong> You could be affected by a lawsuit=
 against Amazon.com, Inc. The Court ordered this notice and decided that th=
e lawsuit should proceed on behalf of a group of people that could include =
you (the =E2=80=9CClass=E2=80=9D). The Court has decided that, unless you r=
equest to opt out (exclude yourself), you are a member of the Class defined=
 as: all persons in the United States who on or after May 26, 2017, purchas=
ed five or more new, physical goods from third-party sellers on Amazon=E2=
=80=99s marketplace.
<br>&nbsp;<br><strong>What is the lawsuit about?</strong> The name of the l=
awsuit is <em>De Coster et al. v. Amazon.com, Inc.</em>, and it is pending =
in the United States District Court for the Western District of Washington =
(Case No. 2:21-cv-00693-JHC).<br><br>
A group of consumers (=E2=80=9CPlaintiffs=E2=80=9D) have filed a class acti=
on lawsuit against Amazon. The lawsuit alleges that Amazon violated federal=
 antitrust laws by using its market power to impose and enforce an anti-dis=
counting policy on its third-party sellers that allowed Amazon to charge hi=
gher commission fees and caused higher prices for goods sold on the Amazon =
marketplace by third-party sellers. Specifically, Plaintiffs claim that Ama=
zon violated the Sherman Act, 15 U.S.C. =C2=A7 1 <em>et seq.</em> Plaintiff=
s are seeking money damages for purchasers and changes to Amazon=E2=80=99s =
policies and practices. Amazon denies any wrongdoing, and the Court has not=
 yet decided whether Amazon did anything wrong.&nbsp;
<br><br><strong>Who represents the Class?</strong> The Court has appointed =
the law firms of Hagens Berman Sobol Shapiro LLP, Keller Postman LLC, and Q=
uinn Emanuel Urquhart & Sullivan LLP to represent the Class (=E2=80=9CClass=
 Counsel=E2=80=9D). If you are a member of the Class, Class Counsel is repr=
esenting your interests in the lawsuit. You don=E2=80=99t have to pay Class=
 Counsel to participate. You may hire your own lawyer to appear in Court fo=
r you at your own expense.<br><br>
<strong>What are your options?</strong> If you want to be included in the C=
lass and this lawsuit, you do not need to do anything, and you will be lega=
lly bound by all of the Court=E2=80=99s orders and Court=E2=80=99s judgment=
, whether favorable or not. You also keep open the possibility of getting m=
oney or benefits that may come from a trial or settlement. If you do not wa=
nt to participate in this lawsuit against Amazon or if you want to keep any=
 right you may have to sue Amazon on your own over the legal claims in this=
 lawsuit, you need to exclude yourself (=E2=80=9Copt out=E2=80=9D). If you =
exclude yourself, you cannot get money or benefits, if any are awarded, fro=
m this lawsuit in the future. Your request to opt out must be submitted by =
August 31, 2026. Go to <a target=3D"_blank" href=3D"hxxps://www[.]amazonant=
itrustlitigation[.]com/" rel=3D"noopener" style=3D"text-decoration: underli=
ne; color: #0068A5;">www.AmazonAntitrustLitigation.com</a> for more informa=
tion on how to opt out.
<br><br><strong>Where to get more information?</strong> This notice is only=
 a summary. For more information on this lawsuit, please visit <a style=3D"=
text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"hxxps=
://www[.]amazonantitrustlitigation[.]com/" target=3D"_blank">www.AmazonAnti=
trustLitigation.com</a> or call (877) 238-1874.&nbsp;<br><br>
You may also obtain information regarding the lawsuit on the Court docket i=
n this lawsuit, for a fee, through the Court=E2=80=99s Public Access to Cou=
rt Electronic Records (PACER) system at <a target=3D"_blank" href=3D"hxxps:=
//ecf[.]wawd[.]uscourts[.]gov" rel=3D"noopener" style=3D"text-decoration: u=
nderline; color: #0068A5;">hxxps://ecf[.]wawd[.]uscourts[.]gov</a> or by vi=
siting the office of the Clerk of the Court for the United States District =
Court for the Western District of Washington, 700 Stewart Street, Suite 231=
0, Seattle, WA 98101, between 9:00 a.m. to 4:00 p.m.
<br><br>PLEASE DO NOT TELEPHONE OR CONTACT AMAZON, AMAZON=E2=80=99S ATTORNE=
YS, THE COURT OR THE COURT CLERK=E2=80=99S OFFICE TO ASK ABOUT THIS LAWSUIT=
.</p></div></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></tbody></table></=
